## Personality & token strategy

| Layer | Model | Job | Token cost |
|-------|-------|-----|------------|
| Banter / UI copy / agent voice | Cheap local or free-tier | Makes it fun to use | Minimal |
| Routine tasks (summarise, organise, draft) | OpenRouter free tier / small model | Day-to-day work | Low |
| Important decisions, legal case, complex reasoning | Claude / Gemini | Gets it right when it matters | Higher, but rare |

Personality is **not** a skin — each agent has a distinct voice defined in the registry. The cheap model generates the personality; the expensive model generates the substance. User never notices the seam.

