- 🟢 Pauly opens one tab, sees his day: tasks, calendar, habits, streaks
- 🟢 Voice note into Matrix → task appears on dashboard in seconds
- 🟢 Agents run jobs overnight without Pauly being present
- 🟢 Nothing gets lost — every output has a home, is previewable, is searchable
- 🟢 Adding a new agent = add a config entry, not a rebuild
